Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.93,0:00:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,(蓮實 克蕾兒)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,(在丈未面前侵犯我)\N（夫對我已沒與趣）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(蓮實 克蕾兒)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 打擾下\N浴室的噴頭球掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:00:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,拜詆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,請問我可以為您服務嗎\N我會讓您滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,浴室的噴頭壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,打電話找人來維修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,說好的1小時就到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒想到真的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,太神速了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上就修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,太厲害了 我太崇拜了\N喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事\N這是他的職責所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的回報太繁瑣 很難懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在公司像你這樣報告工作\N早就被炒魷魚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天都在努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你相比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,太悠閒了吧\N抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,(丈夫對我已沒興趣)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 沒睡醒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,跟夫人性愛太頻繁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,美女 身材太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真羡慕你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 下次老婆借我玩玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我過來看看情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,噴頭沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,已經修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,請你洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我來確認噴頭是否修好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人 請冼澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,請洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:08:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
