Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
