Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,拜詆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊
