Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.17,0:32:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要繼續了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.64,0:33:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要射啦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.31,0:33:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,射入小穴了\N不要 不要射啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.18,0:33:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了\N不要
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.05,0:33:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要射啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.26,0:33:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙 不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.26,0:33:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙\N要射
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.06,0:33:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.00,0:33:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要射
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.18,0:34:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,爽嗎
